          "description": "You stand in an east to west mountain pass. The mountains to your north are scarred giants, but the smaller mountains to your south get even smaller as you look to the west. A path winding upward ascends eastward, toward a broken archway high above. To the north a cart-marked trail leads into the mountains, and just below you a narrow shaft plunges underground. A narrow seam of copper glints from the rock face.",
