        "1014": {
          "vnum": 1014,
          "name": "Foothills",
          "description": "Travel is fairly easy in these rolling hills. They are fairly barren, with some clumps of bunch-grass being the only vegetation. To the east is a mountain pass; vast plains spread out to the west. *A silvery-green herb grows in a dense patch, its leaves fragrant and bitter.*",
