        "293": {
          "vnum": 293,
          "name": "Pine Forest",
          "description": "A thick carpet of pine needles carpet the trail you tread upon. There is no wind here and the air is thick with the sharp, spicy scent of pine. The trees are closely clustered, yet you appear to be able to pass north, west. A long, slender path southward leads into a mixture of pine and oak.",
          "grid_x": 0,
          "grid_y": 1,
          "exits": {
            "n": {
              "to_vnum": 294,
              "to_zone": "Northern Mountains",
              "to_room_name": "Among the Thin Trees",
              "direction": "n",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "294": {
          "vnum": 294,
          "name": "Among the Thin Trees",
          "description": "The altitude is pretty high here so the trees around you are all conifers, and spindly ones at that. As you look into the far distance of the north, you see that the trees evidently disappear as the landscape rises. A wide, comfortable trail leads north and south, and a shadowed trail leads to the east. You are riding atop a well-bred horse.",
          "grid_x": 0,
          "grid_y": 0,
          "exits": {
            "n": {
              "to_vnum": 295,
              "to_zone": "Northern Mountains",
