        },
        "295": {
          "vnum": 295,
          "name": "Treeline",
          "description": "You have reached the altitude where just a few misshapen trees manage to cling to life. A steep trail climbs up into some hills to the north. The land descends to the south and you see a greater abundance of trees in that direction. A thin trail leads along a wooded ridge to the west. You are riding atop a well-bred horse.",
