        "2067": {
          "vnum": 2067,
          "name": "Narrow Cleft",
          "description": "Here the rocks close, blocking further passage into the cleft. Small, furry creatures have built several nests in the sheltered niches of the cleft, and scurry at your intrusion. The winds whistle to the west, pulling with them an odd, foul scent which drifts up through a large crack in the rocks nearby.",
