        "2228": {
          "vnum": 2228,
          "name": "Mountain Path",
          "description": "The wind blows fiercely cold here, as if it were being channeled along this mountain trail. Looking south, you can see that the path rises slightly to the tip of a promontory. The trail also continues north.",
